com.google.android.exoplayer2.source.chunk

Class BaseMediaChunk

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.android.exoplayer2.source.chunk.Chunk
      • com.google.android.exoplayer2.source.chunk.MediaChunk
        • com.google.android.exoplayer2.source.chunk.BaseMediaChunk
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Loader.Loadable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ContainerMediaChunk, SingleSampleMediaChunk

    public abstract class BaseMediaChunk
extends MediaChunk
    A base implementation of MediaChunk, for chunks that contain a single track.

    Loaded samples are output to a DefaultTrackOutput.
